Creacte package.json
    yarn init -y 

instalando libs

yarn add @babel/core @babel/preset-env @babel/preset-react webpack webpack-cli

yarn add react react-dom 

configurar o babel 

yarn add babel-loader -D

testar

src 
const soma = (a, b) => a + b
alert(soma(1, 3))

yarn build 


fazenro auto reload 

yarn add webpack-dev-server -D

depois instalando
yarn dev


fazendo load css babel
yarn add  style-loader css-loader -D

fazendo loader imagem css babel
yarn add file-loader -D